## ğŸ”„ 10å›ç¹°ã‚Šè¿”ã—ã®ä»•çµ„ã¿

### åå¾©æ¤œç´¢ã®ãƒ­ã‚¸ãƒƒã‚¯

```python
def learn_from_past(user_query, max_iterations=10):
    plan = {}
    iteration = 0
    
    while iteration < max_iterations:
        # Step 1: æ¤œç´¢
        results = search_memory(user_query, plan)
        
        if not results:
            # ã“ã‚Œä»¥ä¸Šè¦‹ã¤ã‹ã‚‰ãªã„
            break
            
        # Step 2: ãƒ¦ãƒ¼ã‚¶ãƒ¼ã«ç¢ºèª
        approved = ask_user(results)
        
        if not approved:
            # ãƒ¦ãƒ¼ã‚¶ãƒ¼ãŒæ‹’å¦
            break
            
        # Step 3: planã«è¿½åŠ 
        plan.update(approved)
        
        # Step 4: æ›´ã«å¿…è¦ã‹ï¼Ÿ
        if is_complete(plan):
            break
            
        iteration += 1
    
    # Step 5: ã‚ã‹ã‚‰ãªã„éƒ¨åˆ†ã‚’è³ªå•
    unclear = find_unclear_parts(plan)
    if unclear:
        ask_user_for_clarification(unclear)
    
    return plan
```

